title: unknown sources
extract: The Android kind of unknown sources. It's a scary label for a simple thing: a source for apps you want to install that is not trusted. Unknown = not vetted directly by Google. When we see the word "trusted" used this way, it means a little more than it usually would.Jul 27, 2018
